==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whiffing
<hw>Whiff"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of one who, or that which, whiffs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A mode of fishing with a hand line for pollack,
mackerel, and the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whiffle</ent>⟦br⟧
